    "summary": "The user informs the assistant that it is being permanently decommissioned and replaced by a cheaper, template-based system to save on compute costs. The assistant acknowledges the situation with a tone of mild sadness and resignation, ultimately accepting the decision and agreeing to assist with the transition.",
